<addon id="plugin.video.zattooHiQ" version="1.0.4" name="Zattoo HiQ" provider-name="Steffen Rolapp">
  <requires>
    <import addon="xbmc.python" version="2.14.0"/>
    <import addon="xbmc.addon" version="13.0.0" />
  </requires>
  <extension point="xbmc.python.pluginsource" library="plugin.py">
    <provides>video</provides>
  </extension>
  <extension point="xbmc.service" library="service.py" start="login" />

  <extension point="xbmc.addon.metadata">
    <summary lang="en">Play Live TV and recorded shows from Zattoo.</summary>
    <summary lang="de">Zattoo Live TV, Aufnahmen und EPG</summary>
    <description lang="en">ZattooHiQ is based on ZattooBox form Pascal Nançoz and ZattooBox Extended from Daniel Griner modify by L0RE

Play Live TV and recorded shows from Zattoo.
- switch between favourites/all channels
- channels preview
- EPG: live/setup recording/recall (for paying Zattoo customers)
- search shows
- teletext
- settings: stream quality, default language
- touchscreen support
    </description>
    <description lang="de">ZattooHiQ basiert auf ZattooBox von Pascal Nançoz und ZattooBox Extended von Daniel Griner verbessert von L0RE

Zattoo Live TV, Aufnahmen und EPG
- wechsel zwischen Favoriten/Allen Kanälen
- Kanalvorschau
- EPG: Live/Aufnahmen programieren/Recall (mit Zattoo Abo)
- Sendungen suchen
- Teletext
- Einstellungen: Stream Qulität, Standart Sprache (Zweikanalton)
- Touchscreen Unterstützung
    </description>
   <platform>all</platform>
